# Important Directories in Shift Management System

client/src/lib/components - Frontend: Reusable Svelte UI components
client/src/lib/services - Frontend: API interaction logic
client/src/lib/stores - Frontend: Svelte stores for state management
client/src/routes - Frontend: SvelteKit page routes and server-side logic (+page.svelte, +page.server.js)

server/src/controllers - Backend: Request handling logic (Express route handlers)
server/src/routes - Backend: API route definitions (Express routers)
server/src/db/models - Backend: Database models (Sequelize)
server/src/config - Backend: Configuration files (database, passport, etc.)
server/src/middleware - Backend: Express middleware functions (auth, validation, etc.)
server/src/services - Backend: Business logic services (if separated from controllers)

docs/ - Project documentation (Context, Plan, Guides) 